   - Saving the current position (by seeking to absolute position 0)
   - Writing a header placeholder
   - Writing body content
   - Seeking back to the beginning
   - Updating the header with the actual value

The implementation follows all the assessment objectives and uses the correct function signatures and data types from the Hexi library reference materials.

